
This configuration drives a 3-axis stepper machine using a Mesa Anything
IO board with the HostMot2 firmware.  No limit switches are used, so
this should work with very basic hardware.

Card       Encoders  PWMs  StepGens   Notes 
4i65          0       0       3
4i68          0       0       3
5i20          0       0       3
5i22-big      0       0       3       For the 1.5M gate version
5i22-small    0       0       3       For the 1.0M gate version
5i23          0       0       3
7i43-big      0       0       3       For the 400k gate version
7i43-small    0       0       3       For the 200k gate version

The config will only run if you have the card installed.
